<sect1 id="manuals-texinfo-intro">

    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
        The texinfo backend encapsulates specificities needed to
        create and maintain documentation manuals in Texinfo format.
        This way, through texinfo backend, people can concentrate on
        writing documentation and forget structuring tasks like
        creating files, updating menus, nodes, cross references and be
        aware of where to put the related files.
    </para>

</sect1>
